Let me tell you a little bit

00:01:49.780 --> 00:01:51.120
about the poetry
literature center

00:01:51.120 --> 00:01:52.700
at the Library of Congress.

00:01:52.700 --> 00:01:55.530
We are home to the Poet
Laureate Consultant in Poetry.

00:01:55.530 --> 00:01:58.270
The only federally funded
